WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.500
Even in 1973, it wasn’t always easy 

00:03.700 --> 00:08.000
to bend gender stereotypes and leave your audience awestruck. 

00:09.000 --> 00:16.500
This Natasha Korniloff designed black fishnet spider web and gold creation certainly achieved that goal 

00:17.000 --> 00:23.000
when Bowie shocked the American audience of an NBC TV appearance by wearing it. 

00:23.500 --> 00:29.500
Little did they know that the original outfit had a third hand grabbing Bowie’s crotch

00:30.000 --> 00:34.000
 - an item he judiciously removed to avoid starting a riot.